  <brief_title>Transanal Tube Drainage in Endoscopic Submucosal Dissection of the Colorectal Tumor</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transanal Tube Drainage in Endoscopic Submucosal Dissection of the Colorectal Tumor: A Prospective, Multi-Center, Randomized, Open-Label, Parallel Group, Superiority Clinical Trial</official_title>
